* Diana couldn't believe what Rion refused to do, then saw him lift off into 
the air and streak towards the trees, leaving her behind.*

" RION! What about me?!"

* He would already be to the trees by the time she got half way there, and 
her legs were so short that this monster would have caught up to her long 
before that.
Diana whimperd. He abandonded her.
Tears ran down her cheek as she tried to speed up but she was already going 
as fast as she could, and the nightmare was still gaining. It would be on 
her in a moment or two.
Diana suddenly yowled and turned around, hissing and swatting at the monster 
coming at her, jumping ahead with her fur standing on end she swatted at it.
She would have to look after herself now.*
